deals.itemDescription: This is the perfect size (32 oz. / 1L) for a family meal or if you have that craving during the week and don't want to come to the store. The family size is perfect for keeping it in the freezer and eating it whenever you want it. Just leave it at room temperature or add your bowl to a container with hot water and in a few minutes "voila!" you have the perfect Oak at home. *The family size does not come with toppings, only the acai purée.
